# Cloudflare Pages redirects
# https://developers.cloudflare.com/pages/configuration/redirects/
#
# Pages automatically serves /foo.html at /foo and 308-redirects /foo.html -> /foo.
# Canonicals across the site are therefore extensionless; we only need to handle
# trailing-slash variants and legacy aliases here.
#
# Note: apex -> www (funcitygamesnwa.com -> www.funcitygamesnwa.com) cannot be
# configured here — _redirects sources are path-only. Configure that as a
# Cloudflare Redirect Rule at the zone level (dashboard > Rules > Redirect Rules).

# Trailing-slash variants -> canonical extensionless URL
/about/        /about        301
/contact/      /contact      301
/games/        /games        301
/how-it-works/ /how-it-works 301
/locations/    /locations    301
/venues/       /venues       301

# Legacy/convenience aliases
/home /         301
